Feature: Scenario 5

  Scenario: Search for Limerick, One night stay, 2 adults, 1 Room, With Spa
    Given User has accessed Booking.com website
    And I have entered a location of "Limerick"
    And I have entered a month of "February" and a date of "16" and a duration of "17" nights stay
    And I click on the Show More Option on the Facilities Filter Section
    And I click on the Spa checkbox
    Then The search page will be returned displaying "Absolute Hotel Limerick"